Have a TypeScript file configured with Tabs@4
```ts
// IMacLinuxKeyMapping
class A {
	/**
	 * used only for debug purposes.
	 */
	private readonly _codeInfo: KeyMapping[];
}
```

Select `IMacLinuxKeyMapping` and paste it on top of `KeyMapping`

![indent-on-paste](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/5047891/27638251-e140cb74-5c12-11e7-8376-0a1ab3a47a58.gif)

- VSCode Version: Code 1.13.1 (379d2efb5539b09112c793d3d9a413017d736f89, 2017-06-14T18:13:05.928Z)
- OS Version: Darwin x64 16.4.0
- Extensions: none
---

Steps to Reproduce:

1. add the code `
function * foo(x){
    let y = yield (x+1);
    let z = y + (yield(2));
    console.log(z)
    return y+z;
}
let g = foo(1);
console.log(g.next(1))
console.log(g.next(1))
console.log(g.next(1))
`
2.run `debug`button many times you can see that the anwser is change with time
